        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8057",
        "content": "\"It's a fact,\" said the King.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8057_284428_000052_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8057/284428/8057_284428_000052_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8057",
        "content": "When the final minute is up, we die; but we're obliged to live all of the six hundred years, whether we want to or not.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
